You can give the inputs array-style names that are indexed by `itemnumber`. `$_POST[&#39;buyernumber&#39;]` and `$_POST[&#39;amount&#39;]` will then be arrays, and you can use `$_POST[&#39;submit&#39;]` to get the appropriate array index.

